basically on straddling the difference between finished and done, which tends to work.

24
00:01:42,147 --> 00:01:45,729
in both directions. I end up with teams that say, well, I implemented my last feature,

25
00:01:46,169 --> 00:01:52,933
so I guess I'm done. Or also the reverse, who are the people who say, I know that I

