had a minor freak out about it because consoles have a lot of rules.

52
00:03:49,609 --> 00:03:50,650
Like a lot of rules.

53
00:03:50,730 --> 00:03:56,274
And this is a generic stock photo because we're not allowed to show photos of the binders

